Direct Known Subclasses:
MIterable
public class ExtendedIterable<T>
extends ForwardingIterable<T>

A specific Iterable providing a set of utility methods (most of them are calling their counterparts in Iterables).

To create an ExtendedIterable from an Iterable, you should use the adapt(Iterable) method.

0.3
